import React from 'react'
import { Form, Button, Container } from 'react-bootstrap'


class ProjectForm extends React.Component {

    // STATE
        state = {
            title:'',
            creator: '',
            startDate: '',
            deadLine: '',
            workTime: '',
            commitment: ''
        }
    // handleInputChange
    
    // handleFormSubmit
    


    render() {
        return (
            <React.Fragment>
                <Container>

        <Form>
        <Form.Group controlId="formUserName">
            <Form.Label>Project Administrator</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control 
                type="text" 
                placeholder="Enter username" 
                />
            
        </Form.Group>

        <Form.Group controlId="formProjectTitle">
            <Form.Label>Project Name</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="What are you working on?" />
        </Form.Group>
       
       <Form.Group controlId="formStartDate">
                <Form.Label>Start Date</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="When was this assigned?"/>
       </Form.Group>

       <Form.Group controlId="formDeadLine">
                <Form.Label>Deadline</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="When is this to be completed by?"/>
       </Form.Group>
       <Form.Group controlId="formWorkData">
            <Form.Label>Hours worked per week?</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="work hours" />
            <Form.Label>User Commitment</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="How many hours can you devote per day to this project?" />
       </Form.Group>
       

        <Form.Group controlId="formAddCollabz">
                <Form.Label>Collaborators</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control as="select">
                    <option>select...</option>
                    <option>...</option>
                </Form.Control>
        </Form.Group>

        <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
            Submit
        </Button>
        </Form>
        </Container>

            </React.Fragment>
        );
    };


}

export default ProjectForm
